item.description: I will be departing around 12 noon from the Commuter Lot in Vernon right off of Exit 67 (East or West) on I-84 for the Liberty Clubhouse in Worcester Mass. They are doing phone banking for a get out the vote effort, their primary is this Tuesday! Phone banking is from 1 to 5, I will have to leave around 4:30pm due to a previous engagement but I am very excited to check this place out. Their website is http://www.libertyclubhouse.org. At this point it's just me (Sara is RSVP'd but may or may not make it) and I'm willing to leave a little later if it will help get more people up there. Please call 860-730-3RON to give me a heads up if you want to me to wait a bit for you.
item.name: Phone Banking at the Liberty Clubhouse
